12:29.817 --> 12:31.223
It's not just newspapers.

12:31.226 --> 12:32.912
I found these in his desk, too.

12:39.794 --> 12:42.061
Burn all this...

12:42.097 --> 12:43.396
and anything else you find.

12:43.431 --> 12:45.131
Please.

12:47.602 --> 12:49.669
Your son-in-law has disappeared.

12:49.704 --> 12:52.438
He does that sometimes.

12:57.946 --> 13:00.146
You knew.

13:00.181 --> 13:02.348
You knew what he was doing.

13:02.384 --> 13:05.618
Maria, I am aware of what
goes on in my own home.

13:05.654 --> 13:07.487
Do you share these sympathies with him?

13:07.522 --> 13:11.624
I share his belief that being
born Mexican in this valley

13:11.660 --> 13:13.226
is very bad luck.

